726779f-a.title: Queens: Grand Avenue - 74th Street
726779f-a.text:
Grand Avenue, north side, east of 74th Street, showing the entrance to Washington Park, also known as Seits's Park. Seitz, a brewer, had it built. Auast J. Bruhn was either
an owner or an occupant.
1922
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
